data.description: Located in the sought after Fairview community of Lockport you will fall in love with the potential in which this spacious brick ranch offers. The home is on an extra wide lot, as you walk in you will fall in love with the sundrenched living room which offers eastern exposure and the natural light gleams off the hardwood floors which run throughout the home! The property has a formal dining room, two bedrooms plus den and a full basement! The home offers an attached 1 car garage along with a detached 2 car garage for a total of 3 garage spaces, this is a car collectors dream or the buyer seeking land and a workshop, this is an ideal home in an ideal location! Do not overlook this potential that awaits, homes such as this do not come available often and this one will not last long!
